    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(IS IN ACTIVE DEVELOPMENT)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to <strong>EGGWORLD.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this RPG, you wake up in a <strong>Weird</strong> and <strong>Mysterious</strong> world.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With the help of a sentient talking &quot;Egg<strong>&quot;</strong> sleeping restfully in your pockets you must find your way out of the dark dungeon, <strong>together</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>UNIQUE COMBAT SYSTEM </strong>(Not Turn-Based):</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Charge your Jump-Attacks for extra damage, and dodge enemy attacks.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Original art and soundtrack:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Art and Music created by HUMANS.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Adventure and Explore in this surreal story driven game:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a Strange world with memorable and unique characters.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Created by one person:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A passion project, created with love and care.</p></li></ul>",
